Refs #2628, #2634, #2636, #2637, #2638, #2639, #2667, #2678, #2689, #2695, #2821. Added new values to DurabilityKind_t. Service interfaces defined. SQLite3 service mockup implemented. Added IPersistenceService property to EndpointAttributes. Added log to mockup implementation. Changed load_writer_from_storage parameters (now receives change pool). Added persistence support on writers. Added load_writer_seq_from_storage to IReaderPersistenceService. Added persistence support on readers Added sqlite3 to sources and cmake Added persistence_guid to EndpointAttributes. Changed IWriterPersistenceService to use persistence_guid. Persistent Writer refactor. SQLite3 implementation for writer persistence. Parameter persistence_guid on EndpointAttributes. Added PID_PERSISTENCE_GUID parameter type. Added persistence_guid to WriterProxyData. Added persistence_guid support on StatelessReader. StatelessReader uses persistence_guid for history records. Support for persistence_guid on both readers. Unnecesary method remove from IReaderPersistenceService. Readers table uses string for reader_guid. Implementation of load_reader_from_storage. Renamed persistenceService to persistence_service. Persistent readers refactor. Unnecessary changes reverted. Persistence service refactor (now configured using properties). Added RTPSTest_persistent. Log level of SQLite3PersistenceService changed to info. Added unit tests for persistence service. Refactor to join reader and writer persistence interfaces on a single one. BlackBox tests added. Minor changes and comments. Fixing compiler warnings. Fixing errors detected by tests. Changes to CMake files to include CMAKE_DL_LIBS when linking. Allowing TRANSIENT publishers and subscribers. Coding style fixes. Fixing cmake files. Fixing persistence tests. Blackbox test improvement. Adapting persistence Blackbox tests to develop rebase.
